basics.name: Akkapol “Ek” Kumpapug
basics.headline: AI-Assisted Problem Solver | Research-Driven Thinking | Clear, Practical Execution
basics.about: I am an AI-assisted problem solver with a strong execution background in enterprise systems and internal tools. I use AI primarily to improve the quality of thinking and decision-making, not just to move faster. My focus is on asking better questions, reducing blind spots, and testing assumptions before committing to action. I work with AI as a research and thinking partner to turn ambiguous, messy situations into clear, practical directions that people can actually execute on. With hands-on experience building and operating real systems, I believe long-term value comes from combining modern technology with sound human judgment.
